      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and treated with so much love. Not a single smudge or scratch to be found. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
