    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The double-VANOS system has been recalibrated for optimal cam timing, and the rear subframe has been rigorously inspected for structural integrity. The chassis retains factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a perfectly functioning limited-slip differential and an untouched undercarriage. Every mechanical component operates with surgical precision, offering a pure, analog driving experience that meets the highest standards of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
