    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly museum-grade specimen that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-finish paint completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh scent; the premium leather seats remain supple with zero bolster wear, and every tactile surface\u2014from the knurled knobs to the steering wheel stitching\u2014feels brand new. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance milestone performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or debris. This is not just a car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
